{"tid":1050431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 阿根廷海警開火驅趕中國漁船 非法捕撈","createTime":"2019-03-07T01:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T03:45:41.000Z","uid":224066,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e84880f797fbe5dbd0d4be3ff1405d9bc3f2e472","tid":1050431,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3lkM4t8AaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE3lkM4t8AaA&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b8787608\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3lkM4t8AaA</a><br />\n<br />\n根廷海岸警衛隊上周六（3月2日）凌晨開火驅趕一艘中國漁船，當局懷疑其在阿根廷水域非法捕魚。漁船最終逃脫，阿根廷警方已發出國際拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上周六凌晨，阿根廷海岸警衛隊在聖豪爾赫灣（San Jorge Gulf）附近例行巡邏時，發現中國漁船「HUA XIANG 801」（暫譯：華翔801號）進入阿根廷專屬經濟水域範圍撒開漁網及亮起工作燈，相信是在非法捕魚。<br />\n<br />\n海警巡邏艦分別以英語及西班牙語廣播示警：「如果再不撤退，就會開火」。惟漁船並無回應，反而全速往國際水域駛去。巡邏艦展開追捕，期間漁船更企圖撞向巡邏船。海警決定開火驅趕，經過3小時對峙，漁船最終駛向國際水域。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷警方已向漁船發出國際拘捕令，追緝這艘中國漁船。"},{"pid":"3c6f820e5d6b0d2a1b48b96e213730b520a6693e","tid":1050431,"uid":1672,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:42:32.000Z","msg":"阿根廷未富先驕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76aabd8c024f9152e88f08300ed7385b3b1e1ae4","tid":1050431,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"啲海警廢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 漁船都撚鳩佢哋"},{"pid":"9d4d77ac7ab13bc8ac72a15bbd8d52d931abda88","tid":1050431,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"咁都打佢唔沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿根廷啲海警船好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce00d5799d6192509227fd437b7ad0ae681304dd","tid":1050431,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:46:24.000Z","msg":